name: Fifthroom Markets

overview:
Fifthroom Markets is an online marketplace for home, garden and leisure.

Five specialty shops work together with one check out to let customers browse everything at once or narrow their focus to a specific boutique. Fifthroom Markets’ products include outdoor furniture, patio furniture, garden decor, gazebos, pergolas, garden structures and more.

Fifthroom Markets’ family of websites includes: www.FifthroomMarkets.com www.GazeboCreations.com www.CedarStore.com www.AllPicnicTables.com www.DesignerBridges.com www.TeakDesigns.com
